OL,3,CTrust apologises after nurses claim
OL,4,Ctribunal victory in trans changing
OL,5,Croom row
OL,7,FCounty Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust has issued an apology
OL,9,Fafter an employment tribunal found a
OL,10,Fgroup of nurses had suffered
OL,11,F'harassment' which violated their
OL,12,Fdignity.
OL,14,FA group of nurses from Darlington
OL,15,FMemorial Hospital brought a claim
OL,16,Fagainst County Durham and Darlington
OL,17,FNHS Foundation Trust after Rose
OL,18,FHenderson, who was born male but
OL,19,Fidentifies as a woman, was allowed to
OL,20,Fuse the women's changing facilities.
