OL,4,Ctribunal victory in trans changing
OL,5,Croom row
OL,7,FIn a judgement handed down to the
OL,8,Fparties on Friday 16 January, an
OL,9,Femployment tribunal found the nurses
OL,10,Fsuffered harassment which violated
OL,11,Ftheir dignity and created "a hostile,
OL,12,Fintimidating, humiliating and
OL,13,Fdegrading environment for them"
OL,15,FThe tribunal rejected the nurses'
OL,16,Fclaims that Rose had personally
OL,17,Fengaged in conduct that amounted to
OL,18,Fharassment.
OL,20,FIt also rejected the claim that the
OL,21,Ftrust had victimised the claimants.
