OL,7,FToday, a spokesperson at County Durham
OL,8,Fand Darlington NHS Foundation Trust
OL,9,Fsaid:
OL,11,F"We acknowledge and respect the
OL,12,FEmployment Tribunal's decision
OL,13,Fpublished on Friday 16 January 2026.
OL,14,FWe have a responsibility to provide a
OL,15,Fsafe, respectful and inclusive working
OL,16,Fenvironment for everyone and the
OL,17,FTribunal's findings make clear that we
OL,18,Fdid not get this right for all our
OL,19,Fcolleagues, for which we apologise.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
