OL,7,F"We acknowledge that in our decision
OL,8,Fmaking we did not adequately consider
OL,9,Fthe concerns of a group of our
OL,10,Fcolleagues. In light of the judgement,
OL,11,Fwe will rapidly review our policies
OL,12,Fand the changes that have already been
OL,13,Fput in place and will consider what
OL,14,Ffacilities are required to follow the
OL,15,FTribunal's findings in a way that is
OL,16,Frespectful to all our colleagues.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
