OL,7,F"We know that this has been a
OL,8,Fdifficult and distressing experience
OL,9,Ffor all those involved which we
OL,10,Fregret. We also recognise that the
OL,11,Fimplications of the ruling will affect
OL,12,Fcolleagues in different ways and we
OL,13,Fwant to reaffirm our commitment to a
OL,14,Fsupportive and respectful workplace
OL,15,Ffor all colleagues from all
OL,16,Fbackgrounds."
