OL,7,FDarlington nurse Bethany Hutchison led
OL,8,Fthe claim against County Durham and
OL,9,FDarlington NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,10,Fwas supported by the Christian Legal
OL,11,FCentre.
OL,13,FFollowing Friday's judgement she said:
OL,14,F"This is a victory for common sense
OL,15,Fand for every woman who simply wants
OL,16,Fto feel safe at work.
